<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Blog Master</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .team-member img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .about-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4a00e0, #8e2de2); /* Gradient background */
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .value-card {
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .value-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .value-card i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #8e2de2;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .team-section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<%- include("nav")-%>
    <div class="about-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Our Mission & Vision</h1>
            <p>Empowering bloggers and connecting communities through shared stories.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h2>Our Story</h2>
                    <p>Blog Master was born from a passion for storytelling and a desire to create a vibrant online community. We believe that everyone has a story to tell, and we're here to provide the platform for those stories to be heard.</p>
                    <p>Our journey began with a simple idea: to build a space where writers could express themselves freely and readers could discover diverse perspectives. Today, we're proud to be a growing community of bloggers and readers from around the world.</p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-5">
                    <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="value-card">
                                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                                <h3>Innovation</h3>
                                <p>We constantly seek new ways to improve and innovate.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="value-card">
                                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                                <h3>Community</h3>
                                <p>We foster a supportive and inclusive environment.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="value-card">
                                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                                <h3>Integrity</h3>
                                <p>We operate with honesty and transparency.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



    <!-- Call to Action Section -->
    <div class="container text-center my-5">
        <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
        <p>Subscribe to our newsletter for the latest updates and articles!</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Subscribe Now</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Social Media Links -->
    <div class="container text-center my-5">
        <h4>Follow Us on Social Media</h4>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary mx-2">Facebook</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-info mx-2">Twitter</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-danger mx-2">Instagram</a>
    </div>

    <%- include("footer")-%>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>